<section class="dark on-dark" id="designer">
  <div class="wrap founder-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow on-gold">Meet Your Designer</div>
      <p class="founder-quote">"Most snap-on veneers are an embarrassment. I built one that isn't."</p>
      <div class="founder-body">
        <p>
          Most snap-on veneers are cheaply manufactured plastic, shipped from factories by companies without a
          practicing dentist on the team.
        </p>
        <p>
          Patients walk into my practice wearing them. Within a month, they stop. They're embarrassed by something they
          paid for.
        </p>
        <p>
          That's the gap Revive fills. Every case is designed against my 7-Point Smile Design Protocol.
          <strong>If it doesn't pass, it doesn't ship.</strong> If it arrives and isn't right, we remake it. My name is
          on this because I built it.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="sig-wrap">
        <img
          src="{{'signature.png'|  asset_url}}"
          alt="Dr. Brandon Turley"
          class="sig-img"
          height="100"
          width="100"
        >
        <div class="sig-name">Dr. Brandon Turley, DDS</div>
        <div class="sig-sub">Doctor of Dental Surgery · Founder, Revive Teeth</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="founder-video-col">
      <div class="founder-video">
        <video
          id="founderVideo"
          preload="metadata"
          playsinline=""
          poster="8c0a3ce7-ea3a-4dd3-8d23-308024d240b9"
          src="https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663208502486/UWfZsUxCUvkcxmuP.mp4"
        ></video>
        <div class="fv-overlay" id="fvOverlay">
          <button class="fv-play" aria-label="Play founder video">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M6 4l14 8-14 8z"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fv-cap">Dr. Brandon Turley, DDS · 1 min 52 sec</div>
      <div class="cred-badges">
        <span class="cred-badge">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.9"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"></circle>
            <path d="M12 7v5l3 2"></path>
          </svg>
          12+ Years Practice</span
        >
        <span class="cred-badge">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.9"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path
              d="M12 4c3 0 5 1.6 5 4.5 0 1.6-.5 3-.9 5.2-.4 2.2-.6 5.3-2.1 5.3-1.3 0-1.2-3-2-3s-.7 3-2 3c-1.5 0-1.7-3.1-2.1-5.3C7.5 11.5 7 10.1 7 8.5 7 5.6 9 4 12 4Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          Cosmetic Dentist</span
        >
        <span class="cred-badge">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.9"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M12 3l8 3v6c0 5-3.5 8-8 9-4.5-1-8-4-8-9V6z"></path>
            <path d="M8.5 12.5l2.5 2.5L16 10"></path>
          </svg>
          7-Point Protocol Creator</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
